This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) because it deals with automatic title generation for a given block of text. It may also belong to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) because title generation is a common task in information retrieval. Additionally, the paper's use of a Dependency Tree Compression Model suggests that it may be relevant to Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper's focus on generating titles may also make it relevant to Neural Networks (cs.NE) as title generation is a common task in natural language generation using neural networks.
